  <brief_title>Comparing the Use of Vitamin c (Ascorbic Acid) in Eye Burn in Subconjunctival Injection to Topical or Oral Treatment.</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Subconjunctival Vitamin c on Recovery Rate and End Result From Eye Burn.</official_title>
